mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes sections entitled "As I See It", "Interview - Q & A", "The Dancers Walkthru", "Style Lab", "The Callers Notebook", "Advanced Dancing" and "Vox Saltatoris: The Square Dancer Speaks Up". This edition also contains the articles "In Constructing a Sturdy Tomorrow We Have to Build a Strong Foundation", "Caller's Foundation", "Dancers Vote at the Door", "What's Happening in the Lives of Manning and Nita Smith?", and "Wheelchair Dancers."
